---
title: Fattoush Salad with Crispy Chickpeas, Za’atar-Spiced Pita, and Feta Cheese
description: Fattoush is a Middle Eastern version of the Italian panzanella, a hearty “salad” bulked up with equal parts bread and veggies. In this recipe, toasted pita meets crisp cucumbers meets tangy feta meets a fragrant garlic oil. The result? A salad with major flavor.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/fatoush-salad-595953e7.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/fatoush-salad-b5ae5963.pdf
time required: 35 minutes
